--- Email ---
Default email delivery uses the ProxSave Cloud Relay, with local sendmail as failover.
ProxSave does not collect raw SMTP settings; choose pmf only when Proxmox Notifications is configured.
Enable email notifications? [Y/n]: Email delivery methods:
  relay    ProxSave Cloud Relay over outbound HTTPS (default)
  sendmail Local /usr/sbin/sendmail (fallback/default failover; requires a local MTA)
  pmf      Proxmox Notifications via proxmox-mail-forward (SMTP lives in Proxmox)
